Source link https://github.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/blob/master/docs/deploy/index.md

Prerequisite Generic Deployment Command
The following Mandatory Command is required for all deployments.
kubectl apply -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/nginx-0.29.0/deploy/static/mandatory.yaml

on Bare metal kubectl apply -f 
https://raw.githubusercontent.com/kubernetes/ingress-nginx/nginx-0.29.0/deploy/static/provider/baremetal/service-nodeport.yaml

check installation 
kubectl get pods --all-namespaces 
